<i>noun</i>: 악덕 [악떡], 악 [악] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>악덕 [악떡]</dt><br>
<dd>vice; immorality; corruption</dd><br>
<dd>부도덕하고 나쁜 마음이나 행동.</dd><br>
<dd>An immoral, bad intention or behavior.</dd><br>
<dt>악 [악]</dt><br>
<dd>evil; badness; vice</dd><br>
<dd>올바르지 않고 도덕적 기준에 어긋나 나쁜 것.</dd><br>
<dd>Something not right, bad, and against a moral standard.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>